latestIgtvVideos.title: Skin improvement with Profhilo ft. Dr. Samir
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Since my skin still hasn’t fully recovered after suffering from severe acne. I’m at the Sara clinic, jalandhar for my first sitting of profhilo. It’s basically injectable hyaluronic acid for treating skin issues. It boosts and hydrates the skin and even slows down ageing and sagging. Dr. Samir who is known for his anti ageing skills and has done more than 20,000 procedures till date is going to perform the procedure by injecting it at 5 points on each side of the face. Since Profhilo has a very high concentration of HA it helps in rejuvenating the skin’s ability to produce collagen and elastin which in turn help in achieving youthful, firm and radiant skin. It’s a really quick procedure and doesn’t require numbing. It’s effects stay for more than a year’s time which I think is great. @drsamirarora @almalasers_india 
.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Never ever had the confidence to come on screen without makeup and without any filter. But I love how social media has made me come out of my comfort zone. latestIgtvVideos.title: HAPPY WOMEN’S DAY !
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
One of the things that I’ve realised over time is that women are the most beautiful creation of God. Beautiful multitaskers who manage everything from the smallest needs of their family, to being a boss. To all the women reading this right now. Doesn’t matter if you’re a baker, a designer, an artist, a teacher, a stay-at-home mom or if you’re still trying to figure things out. You’ll do great and you are doing great! No one is you and that is your power! Every women’s success should be an inspiration to another. We’re strongest when we cheer each other. 

And to all the men reading this. Go wish your sister, mother, daughter, wife, aunt,.. if you haven’t already. Because they deserve this and need to be celebrated.

Thank you @heebeecoffee for appreciating my efforts at @youngberry_official 🤍#moresuccesstocome 
.

Day 2 of 6 Days of Hacks 💥| Scarf magic & Old jacket transformation !! 

Today’s reel is all about reimagining the everyday! turning basics into bold fashion moments with a little creativity and zero rules! 💡✨

👚 My Hack: Took a shimmer scarf & transformed it into a statement blouse using… a bangle! Yep, that’s right. Just one accessory and a little twist made this look go from simple to stunning. Perfect for when you want to look effortlessly chic without spending a rupee. 💁‍♀️💫

🧥 His Hack: Revived an old denim jacket by adding cool, custom patches! giving it a fresh, edgy vibe. From dull to dope in minutes. Who says guys can’t DIY too? 🔥
